### 4. Get All Lectures
GET {{baseUrl}}/lectures


### 5. Get Lecture by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/lectures/{{lectureId}}


### 6. Delete Lecture
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/lectures/{{lectureId}}